Er... The CF didn't suffer nearly that much damage, Airshadow. All 
that happened is the bridge got blown to scrap and the hull and outer 
defences got mutilated. The power core needs some serious recharging, 
but the CF has enough solar bateries for that.

::Prowl::

"98 percent?!" Prowl echos back over the comm, surprised. He looks up 
at the Cybertronian Fire. That was definetly not 98 percent damage. 
"Are you sure? Doesn't look as bad as 98 to me."
